N2  - Commentary is presented for a number of articles published in previous issues of ?Academy of Management Review.? They include ?The comparative impact of organization development interventions on hard criteria measures,? by J. M. Nicholas, published in a 1982 issue, ?Understanding radical change: Bringing together the old and new institutionalism,? by R. Greenwood and C. R. Hinings, published in a 1989 issue and ?Some unanticipated consequences of organizational restructuring,? by W. McKinley and A. G. Scherer, published in a 2000 issue.
